comments: Daniels (LAL) and Iwundu (ORL) make marginal contact with one another as they move towards the screen.
Ross (ORL) makes contact to the body of Caldwell-Pope (LAL) prior to his upward shooting motion.
Gordon (ORL) places two hands on James (LAL) during the pick.
Daniels (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Ross (ORL) and cleanly deflects the ball, any additional contact is deemed incidental.
Vucevic (ORL) is firming up and sets a legal pick on Daniels (LAL).
McGee (LAL) makes contact to the body of Gordon (ORL) during his shooting motion.
Vucevic (ORL) briefly places a resting hand to the back of McGee (LAL) during the dunk.
Fultz (ORL) makes some contact to McGee (LAL) after spinning towards the basket.
McGee (LAL) makes incidental contact with the net while contesting Fultz' (ORL) shot attempt. The contact does not cause the rim to rock or vibrate in an unnatural manor.
McGee (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (ORL) during the play.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact to the body of Fultz (ORL) during his shooting motion.
Howard (LAL) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Iwundu (ORL) as they disengage during the screen.
Howard (LAL) and Vucevic (ORL) both engage and disengage during the rebound.
Cook (LAL) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).
Gordon (ORL) crosses the plane of the free throw line prior to the ball touching the basket ring.
